trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint> maintains two <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection> objects: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.MatchingLocations%2A> specifies parameters used for matching activity status events and <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.ExcludedLocations%2A> specifies parameters used to exclude activity status events from matching.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint> mantém dois <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection> objetos: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.MatchingLocations%2A> Especifica os parâmetros usados para eventos de status de atividade de correspondência e <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.ExcludedLocations%2A> Especifica os parâmetros usados para excluir eventos de status de atividade de correspondência.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection" /> class.

trans-unit.source: The default constructor initializes the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection> to an empty list.
trans-unit.target: O construtor padrão inicializa o <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection> para uma lista vazia.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection" /> class by using a list of user locations.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection" /> usando uma lista dos locais de usuário.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection> is initialized to contain the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocation> objects specified in `locations`.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection> é inicializada para conter o <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocation> objetos especificados em `locations`.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="locations" /> is a null reference (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="locations" /> é uma referência nula (<see langword="Nothing" /> no Visual Basic).
